      "comment": "PALAWA KANI (1) returns after a spell of five months. Looking to emulate her win at this track when returning from a spell last prep. Comes here with definite claims while fresh. WISE CHOICE (6) finished third over 1100m here at her most recent appearance on October 16. Has switched to the Kym Afford yard. Has found the right race. ZOE SHARK (2) hasn't been far away recently including last time out when third over 800m at Ipswich. Will find this a little easier than last time and is capable of testing this field. GOODES (4) finished fourth over 800m at Warwick at his most recent appearance on August 6. Has a terrific record here with two wins and a placing from three starts and rates a definite top-three chance.",
